[[File:Raxus_Prime_Hulk_Collector.jpg|thumb|A Hulk Collector on [[Raxus Prime/Legends|Raxus Prime]].]]

The '''Raxus Prime Hulk Collector''' (also called '''hulk compactor''') was a crane-like vehicle that [[Scavenger/Legends|scavenged]] the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Raxus Prime/Legends|Raxus Prime]] looking for spare parts that could be salvaged. It had been created by [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]] in order to recondition obsolete machinery in its junkyards. Those hulk compactors used a large, low-powered tractor beam to pick up hulks of junk, and were equipped with heavy armor.

During the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic's]] [[Conquest of Raxus Prime|conquest]] of the junk world, hulk collectors were a fairly common sight, even being noticed by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] duo [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] during their pursuit of [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|CIS]] [[Single Trooper Aerial Platform/Legends|scouts]]. After the chase, they were encountered again during an ambush of a Separatist supply convoy en route to an excavation site.

